{"tid":1672142,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"百人「重慶」大合唱感謝南亞戰友","createTime":"2019-10-24T02:37:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T03:31:35.000Z","uid":25558,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"da1852485e9735d29ec7113def94050e68b17cf4","tid":1672142,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T02:37:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20191024/20792801\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191024%2F20792801&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUoaVJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=45a0a60b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191024%2F20792801&h=e25f9852\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20191024/20792801</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n百人「重慶」大合唱感謝南亞戰友<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191024/large/1571847777_eb4b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191024%2Flarge%2F1571847777_eb4b.gif&h=04aefe2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n逾百市民到重慶大廈外快閃唱歌，答謝少數族裔對港人抗爭活動的支持。翁志偉攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】20多人響應號召到重慶大廈外快閃「和你唱」，以歌曲答謝少數族裔人士對抗爭活動的支持。周日有份派水的印度裔社工Jeffrey Andrews成為聽眾，認為「香港人有好特別嘅DNA&hellip;&hellip;跌低一定企得返起身」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191024/large/1571847776_c251.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191024%2Flarge%2F1571847776_c251.gif&h=444b8bc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港人與少數族裔人士舉起We connect標語，象徵彼此為同路人。<br />\n<br />\n「團結使我們強大」<br />\n<br />\n民陣召集人岑子杰上周疑遭南亞裔兇徒襲擊，令清真寺及重慶大廈在周日遊行中成為焦點，當日有少數族裔人士在重慶大廈外派水和唱歌。20多人昨晚響應網上號召參與「重慶大廈大合唱」，答謝少數族裔支持。<br />\n<br />\n他們唱出《願榮光歸香港》、《光輝歲月》、《海闊天空》、《地厚天高》中梁天琦唱過的《十八》，又舉起「Solidarity makes us strong（團結使我們強大）」和「We all are Hongkoners」標語，象徵彼此為同路戰友。<br />\n<br />\n合唱不足半小時，聚集逾百人圍觀合唱，有南亞裔人士旁觀和舉手和應。有份參與的楊先生稱，在不同遊行均常見南亞裔人士的蹤影，故特意到場答謝，稱很多少數族裔幾代在港扎根，「我當佢哋香港人！」印度裔社工Jeffrey Andrews曾探望岑子杰，他一度擔心重慶大慶或清真寺會被破壞，最後壞事變好事，令少數族裔更受其他港人接受。最終破壞清真寺的不是示威者而是警方，令他大嘆「Oh My Gosh（我的天）」。不過警方已經道歉，他表示接受，「佢哋係承認做錯咗嘢，我哋都要有嗰個心去接受番」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者盧珮瑤 <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n只求重啟政改 真正一國兩制<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n千人鏈向英爭取第二國籍"},{"pid":"fc774691026c59981f920b72b17ad2f67d435a10","tid":1672142,"uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T02:38:54.000Z","msg":"尖沙咀重慶大廈大合唱<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_sx4SC4nk6E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_sx4SC4nk6E&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUoaVJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=ccbeef04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_sx4SC4nk6E</a>"},{"pid":"153484dfc5dfefe47038bc5a03bb420b26fb6ce5","tid":1672142,"uid":114186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T02:55:03.000Z","msg":"警蛆幾時有道歉"},{"pid":"40e84a84c6d443a368eb9b85f4e00e1cd9c2b482","tid":1672142,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T03:01:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b632d2335b728175a80a4f5e5ff22b8d9ed931fa","tid":1672142,"uid":150742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T03:13:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdd28a6905df6f046609b397dfc89e326bdb3dbf","tid":1672142,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T03:30:47.000Z","msg":"前線咁多南亞義士, 點可以唔connect?"},{"pid":"54eee53f2cc6678c07d38d89ffa68c1811577520","tid":1672142,"uid":93962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T03:31:35.000Z","msg":"推"}]}